    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Pavu, a mystical place filled with stunning landscapes, intriguing ruins, intelligent robots and mystical artifacts. In a dystopian future where nature and technology coexist in harmony, until the arrival of Kurumi, a boy who challenges this balance by revealing the mystery surrounding the disappearance of an ancient human civilization and the origin of the machine society.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >             <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164030/extras/57e0b319e58c413ec91c0fe71f8faa73.poster.avif?t=1745353293\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164030/extras/57e0b319e58c413ec91c0fe71f8faa73.webm?t=1745353293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164030/extras/6f4c545475970fc84abc9d3e1153bcb0.avif?t=1745353293\" width=800 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To survive in Pavu you need to master its strategic combat. Dodge, block, and attack! Face the various Robots, discovering their weaknesses, finding and improving equipment, acquiring unique abilities and building your own play style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164030/extras/923b6ef1307bd5b42985af535954d47c.poster.avif?t=1745353293\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164030/extras/923b6ef1307bd5b42985af535954d47c.webm?t=1745353293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164030/extras/74f9053fa34ea8145a2250556136f6ff.avif?t=1745353293\" width=800 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the journey of Kurumi, a newly awakened boy in search of answers about himself and humanity in a fantastical land full of robots, traps and encounters, once inhabited by a vanished human civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164030/extras/8453e55ac95efdcf82a9d3c08d9ac27e.poster.avif?t=1745353293\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164030/extras/8453e55ac95efdcf82a9d3c08d9ac27e.webm?t=1745353293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164030/extras/aea3f60cea7aa4871ad8818920f413f4.avif?t=1745353293\" width=800 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mixing elements of fantasy and science fiction with Brazilian culture and nature, the world of Pavu was entirely handmade, seeking to create a picturesque world, where each place has a story and a reason to exist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
